{"title":"王进喜","authors":["戴奇林"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":6,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王进喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴奇林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与铁合在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人就有了硬度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就没有打不穿的油井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁就有了灵性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻头专往有油的地方打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与石油打了一辈子交道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的话也有石油味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一遇火就能燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种动力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说你是一台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知休息的钻机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁味十足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如钻杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直来直去宁折不弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是默默地旋转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺进挺进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中国沾满油污的耻辱打穿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻杆能到达的深度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你的深度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脊梁如钻塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风骨明透"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹不倒雨打不垮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座钻塔就是一座丰碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔的高度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你的高度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国最需要能源的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是一口采之不竭的油井"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}